; L9: Ramp + Conveyor Combo
; Grid: 11-col x 5-row playable (x: 0-10, y: 0-4)
; Player at (1,1), Box at (2,2) top=IMPACT_A
; Ramp at (3,2) dir=RIGHT → rolling RIGHT: IMPACT→NORMAL ✓
; Conveyors at (5,2),(7,2) going RIGHT
; Goal button at (10,2) requires NORMAL
; Solution: push RIGHT→ramp (NORMAL)→conveyor→conveyor→button→goal

